magnemite/magneton are genderless

Confusion is 50% chance of hitting themself for 1-4 turns
	-damage is equal to a self hit with 40 power physical
	
Standard crit is 1/16
Increased crit is 2/16
STAB (same type attack bonus) is 50% power buff

